'''额内回'''（{{lang-en|Medial frontal gyrus}}）是[[大脑|大脑]][[额叶|额叶]]的一个结构，是[[额上回|额上回]]在[[大脑半球|大脑半球]]的内侧面延展<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Medial frontal gyrus {{!}} Radiology Reference Article {{!}} Radiopaedia.org|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/medial-frontal-gyrus?lang=us#:~:text=The%20medial%20frontal%20gyrus%20is,contains%20the%20supplementary%20motor%20area.|accessdate=2021-04-09|last=Gaillard|first=Frank|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Medial Frontal Gyrus - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/medial-frontal-gyrus|accessdate=2021-04-09|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect|language=en}}</ref>。严格上，额内回和额上回有所不同，但结构上相连<ref name=":0" />。额内回后部与[[中央旁沟|中央旁沟]]相连，与[[中央旁小叶|中央旁小叶]]相隔<ref name=":02">{{Cite web|title=Paracentral sulcus|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/paracentral-sulcus?lang=us|accessdate=2021-04-10|last=Croft|first=Timothy|work=|publisher=Radiopaedia|language=en-US}}</ref>。

== 功能 ==
额内回在[[人腦|人脑]]的[[决策|决策]]制定和执行机制中扮演角色<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Action sets and decisions in the medial frontal cortex|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15350242/#:~:text=A%20medial%20superior%20frontal%20gyrus,and%20errors,%20and%20in%20guiding|last=Rushworth|first=M. F. S.|last2=Walton|first2=M. E.|date=2004-09|journal=Trends in Cognitive Sciences|issue=9|doi=10.1016/j.tics.2004.07.009|volume=8|pages=410–417|issn=1364-6613|pmid=15350242|last3=Kennerley|first3=S. W.|last4=Bannerman|first4=D. M.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Functional specialization within the medial frontal gyrus for perceptual go/no-go decisions based on "what," "when," and "where" related information: an fMRI study|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16102231/|last=Talati|first=Ardesheer|last2=Hirsch|first2=Joy|date=2005-07|journal=Journal of Cognitive Neuroscience|issue=7|doi=10.1162/0898929054475226|volume=17|pages=981–993|issn=0898-929X|pmid=16102231}}</ref>。

